{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act33side", "eventName": "巴別塔", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BB-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "悠長的旅途", "storyInfo": "博士帶著阿米婭回到了巴別塔，決定以巴別塔一員的身分幫助阿米婭和其他感染者。特蕾西婭則向博士展示了自己利用源石創造的“希望”。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "1091年秋"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，巴別塔羅德島本艦"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可露希爾，進度如何？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不希望這次還會出現本艦核心系統失控的問題。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_050", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……哈哈，你非要說呢，那可能還是遇到了一些小小的問題來著。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算拿著你給我的錦囊妙計，PRTS的很多程式加密模式也不是常人能理解的啊。我的解碼儀器還不能完全適配。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就結果而言，可能來不及在博士登艦前完全關閉系統。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再嘗試一次。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果還是沒有把握，就準備應急方案……完全切斷本艦的所有能源。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心交給我吧！", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過……看來你還藏了很多秘密呢，凱爾希。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來沒有見過有人能讓你如此緊張。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這不重要，可露希爾。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重要的是，我不希望本艦出現任何意外。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，可按照阿斯卡綸傳回的任務簡報來看，博士只是一個普通人，還是一個會背著落難小兔子到處瞎逛的大善人。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們好像沒有必要這麼防備他吧？", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威脅並不來自博士。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是什麼？", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還不需要知道。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了博士的安全，也為了巴別塔成員的安全，抹除他的登艦記錄。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在博士和特蕾西婭得出結論前，不必讓其他成員知道他的存在。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好好，我再努力努力……", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是明明你一副很在意博士的樣子，卻又這麼警惕那個人……", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——難道博士抓住了你的什麼把柄！", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要想著調查，你查不到。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃。不用這麼嚴肅吧。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有……那個被救下的孩子，她的身分？", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是老結論。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我反覆核對了當時與雷姆必拓有關的一切記錄，還讓Scout和軍事委員會的內應做了確認。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭的身分沒有問題。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的父母的確是在為我們運送雷射開採模組的車隊裡遇襲身亡，針對他們的襲擊是絕對的意外。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人知道他們運送的是和薩卡茲有關的貨物，而那場襲擊也並非軍事委員會的刻意安排。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而她應該也是在這場事故中才成了感染者。如果不是博士……她可能會在雷姆必拓淒慘地度過餘生吧。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會親自負責那個孩子登艦後的檢查和治療方案。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是不放心那個孩子嗎？", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不放心。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她年紀太小，感染礦石病後沒經過像樣的治療。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是這種“不放心”喔。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不希望博士的善意變成拖延她治療的罪魁禍首，而且……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……特蕾西婭會說，她是個善良的孩子，有權利選擇未來。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "38_g20_skyblue_L1/38_g20_skyblue_r1/38_g20_skyblue_L2/38_g20_skyblue_r2", "solidwidth": "1280/1280/1280/1280", "solidheight": "720/720/720/720"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 60.0, "yFrom": 500.0, "yTo": 720.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，阿米婭。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好睏……我……我在哪？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士……博士？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士就在這。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小懶蟲，快醒醒，你快要到家了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迷迷糊糊地，阿米婭感受到溫暖的指尖在臉頰旁移動。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好癢，哈哈，不要撓我的脖子。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀！", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你是誰？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭。我是特蕾西婭。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭……博士和我提起過你……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，博士怎麼說我呢？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，忘記了……不過我當時在吃很好吃的胡蘿蔔蛋糕……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭應該是……香香的……甜甜的……熱騰騰的。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那現在呢？特蕾西婭和你想像的樣子一樣嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……也是香香的……甜甜的……熱騰騰的，就是沒有胡蘿蔔味……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，看來還沒睡醒呢。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小阿米婭，要和我們一起回家嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家……嗯……好……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_closeeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，巴別塔羅德島本艦外"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭的懷中，小小的卡特斯正環著她的脖子酣睡。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她輕輕拍拍阿米婭的後背，轉頭看向一旁顯得有些疲憊的博士。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你專程離艦來接我們……特蕾西婭。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你也不是無所不知的，博士。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少在照顧小孩子這方面，你還有很多要學的東西。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……當然。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看上去和離開時很不一樣了，博士。這趟旅程怎麼樣？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見到了很多，也學到了很多……在這片大地上所見到的都很有趣。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，我遇見了阿米婭……在那場事故中救下她，簡直算得上奇蹟。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭。她的確比信中寫的還要可愛。可憐的孩子，但也算幸運。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的病情不可避免地在變嚴重，我需要帶她回來接受治療。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我離開的這段時間，巴別塔……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算不上順利，我們遇到了許多問題，但並不急在這一時去解決。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經過那麼漫長的旅途，你們一定很累了，請先休息一下吧。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常感謝，特蕾西婭。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，我們到家了。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……博士，你在叫我嗎……我是不是睡著了？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀，小阿米婭，你醒了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，下來好不好？特蕾西婭一直抱著你會累的。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭乖巧地點點頭，從特蕾西婭的懷中躍下，站在地上蹦了蹦。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-100,0"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那阿米婭可以牽著我嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士……？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以的。特蕾西婭是我的朋友，是值得信任的人，之後，她也會陪著你很長時間。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是巴別塔嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好大啊，比那些採礦地塊還要大……原來博士以前生活在這種地方。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這裡生活了很久……很久，阿米婭。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是博士的家嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，阿米婭，這裡是博士生活過很久的家。對吧，博士？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是的。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以後這裡也會是你的家，讓我們和博士一起照顧你，好不好？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……博士在哪，我就在哪。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rampartclose"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 1.0, "grad": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i15", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 6.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 2.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.0, "block": "false", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope02_intro", "key": "$newhope02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們踏上了眼前的升降平台，巴別塔的標誌緩緩出現在他們的眼前。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那扇沉重的大門緩緩打開，迎接著他們的到來。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭感受到了阿米婭的膽怯，輕輕扶住了她的肩膀。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這扇門後面……是什麼樣啊？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那後面，都是歡迎阿米婭與博士的人。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會猶豫嗎，特蕾西婭？正式接納我，還有這個孩子。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼好猶豫的呢？我很高興，巴別塔可以成為很多人的家。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過，這裡許多人都還不認識你，接下來你恐怕會度過很忙碌的幾天了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應該以什麼身分出現在他們面前？", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這的確很傷腦筋。但我想，你可以先和凱爾希聊聊，她一直在等著你。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你的顧慮，你的疑問，還有你藏在心底裡的秘密，去和凱爾希說說吧。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則她會很難過的。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你本可以……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的希望“魔王”來揭開你不願傾訴的心思，我會這麼做的。但我感覺到，你還在猶豫。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，阿米婭，博士，讓我們去見她。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gatecloz"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭。你就是阿米婭，對嗎？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希蹲了下來，從口袋掏出一顆早已備好的糖果遞給女孩。"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，感謝你一路上保護著博士。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝……凱爾希醫生。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以去找特蕾西婭小姐嗎？我們得為你做一些檢查。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "檢查……會痛嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會痛，但我知道你是堅強的孩子，博士已經寫信告訴我了。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士會陪著我嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，不過博士有一些工作需要先處理。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的阿米婭。在病房裡等我一會，我很快就會去找你的。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，之後你也需要做全身的檢查。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……博士。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之後你還打算再離開嗎？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會了，我想這趟旅程已經足夠。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你已經下定決心的話，我尊重你的選擇。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，你很在意阿米婭的健康……哪怕她與你本無交集。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些新生命與我們也並無本質差異。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……很高興。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你始終選擇了希望。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎回來，Dr.{@nickname}。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_infirmary", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "channel": "bgs", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭還好嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血液裡源石含量始終很高，目前阻斷劑的效力還遠遠達不到控制病情的程度。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "必須要研發新一代的藥物……我需要一些資源和時間。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巴別塔的所有資源自始至終都向你敞開，博士。我們很樂意向你開放現階段對於礦石病的所有研究。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……作為交換，我能幫上你和凱爾希什麼忙？", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並非交換，這是巴別塔建立的初衷之一，我們會力所能及地幫助每一個礦石病患者。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從凱爾希喚醒你的那天起，我就相信你會幫助我們所有人，就像你會幫助阿米婭那樣。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，或許我現在終於有機會問你那個問題。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你如何看待這片大地？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想我還沒有資格去點評些什麼。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "文明並沒有高低優劣之分，如今的泰拉文明，同樣是經歷漫長且艱辛的時光才演變成現在的樣子。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而源石又和所有生命開了一個無比惡劣的玩笑……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得你說過，現在的源石並不符合最初的預期。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我原本的期待裡，它本不該帶來這些苦難。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（睡夢中的囈語）", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能感覺到，你隱藏著一些秘密。可是你心底那股我無法理解的……悲憫，也絕非作假。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想修復這個錯誤，可現在的我無能為力……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況文明的進程大都相似，無論人們如何掙扎，無論其光芒在某一瞬間有多麼璀璨……終點恐怕都顯而易見。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可凱爾希說過，在最後的日子裡，你們亦不曾放棄希望。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在最後的歲月裡，我同樣有許多朋友，他們面臨著遠超你想像的難題和困擾，也心懷著……比你們有過之而無不及的鬥志和希望。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可他們，也無一例外，失敗，消亡。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……特蕾西婭。我們相處的時間還不算長，我想知道，你做這一切的信念是什麼？", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巴別塔向軍事委員會妥協，是為了等一個什麼樣的結果？", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我有東西想給你看。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於源石，我們遲早都要向你請教答案。這也是凱爾希喚醒你的原因。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你能來看看……我短暫努力的結果。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_thundercloud", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們快要到了……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這附近只有一片荒蕪，甚至在天災多發地區都算得上極端。但看得出，可露希爾甚至有抽出空來維護這條小徑，危險的小道……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石簇之間的分叉小徑，特蕾西婭，你的秘密也不比我少。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰讓我是“魔王”呢。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，接下來你看到的東西，請不要跟任何人說起。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i22", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ghosthunter_intro", "key": "$ghosthunter_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在源石晶簇遍布的荒野上跋涉許久，訪客見到了一小片花圃。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在天災中央，在毀滅之間，在晚霞與星河都尋覓不到的無名原野上。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星星點點的白色小花圈出了一方遺世獨立的聖地，與周遭的環境隔絕開來。蠻荒的一切都與這裡無關，連風也變得柔軟。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是被時間遺忘的溫室，保留著遙遠的過去纖塵不染的模樣。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是人類第一次從神明那裡偷來火光，照亮了蒼茫夜空的一角。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭捧起了一朵純白的花。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是我，也是巴別塔對源石最深入的研究。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花……？", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，是“源石”。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該能意識到，這並不是催出花朵的源石技藝。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來自源石之中的訊息，來自內化宇宙的反轉……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們對源石的研究，已經到了這一步？什麼時候……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲是最了解源石的種族，即便如此，比起源石的全部，我們所知不過是冰山一角。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使有凱爾希協助我們鑽研源石的本質，我們費盡心思、窮盡心血所做到的，也僅僅是將一塊巴掌大的活性源石，轉化為這樣的……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一片花圃。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一種希望。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這朵小小的白花，只是我的一點努力。我也想請求博士你的幫助。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想看花海倒灌，湧出卡茲戴爾的斷崖和山谷，直到開滿大地的那一天。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那個未來，值得我們去冒險。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，正如你所見，卡茲戴爾，長久以來都陷在戰爭的泥沼中。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少當下，我想用源石的這種能力，為卡茲戴爾開闢一片可以不受外敵侵擾的家園。人們可以留在這裡安居樂業，不用再以戰場為家。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在更遙遠的將來……如果有一天，我們可以完全控制源石，整片大地的模樣都會被改變吧。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如天災發生時，天空中落下的不是源石晶簇，而是軟綿綿的雲朵。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如感染者身上也不再長出石頭……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概不會有人做這樣荒唐的幻夢吧……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……作為一個薩卡茲，你確實與眾不同，特蕾西婭。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開滿大地的花……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那會是一副生機勃勃的景象。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼……是這樣一朵花？", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……沒什麼特別的原因，峽谷外面生長著這種花，我第一次尋找合適的實驗地點時，看到了而已。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是無意的。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希說，這種花曾有個名字，叫夏雪草。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過經歷了這麼多年的環境變化，它也在適應，也許，它也可以有一個新的名字。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得呢，博士？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "新的道路正在打開。", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_white", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>一條自毀之路。</color>", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭，能聽到嗎？", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在聽。我正在帶博士參觀我們的……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾傳回來一些緊急訊息，必須立刻讓你知曉。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……與維多利亞有關。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}